metadata.name: The Divine Feminine
metadata.description:
Your pain is our pain,  
we will not let you fall.  
for we are all different, yet connected. 
placed on this earth to protect, to create, to bring life.  
without Her, there is no life source. 
there is no balance. 
much like the Ophanim Angel, we are of peace, humility & submission, yet fire is within us. 
our power is infinite 
the only portal between heaven and earth, the beauty, the strength, the nurturing, 
The Divine Feminine.
